  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.9.1">
<l>calaṅkoṇṭa viraṇiyaṉa takalmārvaṅ kīṇṭu taṭaṅkaṭalaik kaṭaintamutaṅ koṇṭukanta kāḷai</l>
<l>nalaṅkoṇṭa karumukilpōl tirumēṉi yammāṉ nāṭōṟum makiḻntiṉitu maruviyuṟai kōyil</l>
<l>calaṅkoṇṭu malarcoriyum mallikaiyoṇ cerunti caṇpakaṅkaḷ maṇanāṟum vaṇpoḻili ṉūṭē</l>
<l>valaṅkoṇṭu kayalōṭi viḷaiyāṭu nāṅkūr vaikunta viṇṇakaram vaṇaṅkumaṭa neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Simple heart, worship in Vaikunta Viṇṇakaram in Nānkūr</l>
<l rend="indent">where kayal fish play, darting with boldness</l>
<l rend="indent">in the midst of the fertile garden with [pools of] water,</l>
<l>Where the scents of jasmine which showers blossoms, brilliant pear,</l>
<l rend="indent"> [and] champaka waft,</l>
<l>The temple where dwells our lord, happily with affection</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] rejoicing daily, whose divine body is like a dark cloud</l>
<l rend="indent">which brings prosperity,</l>
<l>The youth who was pleased, churning the wide sea [and] bringing nectar,</l>
<l rend="indent">having [once] split the broad chest of Hiraṇya who bore [him] hatred.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
